Hi,

the game crashed to the blue screen the last time I played and now I get the title message when trying to load the game under 'Resume saved game'. The game was running pretty stable even though I have a ton of mods (well, a crash now and then but nothing serious). I have not installed any new mod recently.

I hope someone can help me. I'm playing 0.25 version of the 32 bit version of KSP.

Anybody here who can help we save my save game? Or that could guide me to help myself?
You're running KSP 0.25? Make sure none of your plugins are for .90.

You should post your player.log. If there is anything serious, it will usually be right in there.

You know what, i've actually been wondering that too! If anyone knows, I'd be very grateful.

Hi Nathan, thanks for helping me. I was down with fever the last few days and didn't feel like doing anything on the computer. All mods are on 0.25 that have a mod for that which are not all. For example fuel science hails from 0.23, modular multi vehicles from 0.24. However from the 3 saves that I have for 0.25 only the one which was accessed during a computer crash is now unaccessible (see screenshot here: https://www.dropbox.com/s/2s029ieugsm6zz0/screenshot123.jpg?dl=0 ). Also I played 100+ hours with my mods and the game ran fine then.
